1. Check if the VLANs exist and which ports are in them

#show vlan brief

2. Check one specific VLAN

#show vlan id 40

3. Check trunk ports (links between switches or to router)

#show interfaces trunk

4. Check the configuration and mode of a specific port

# show interfaces GigabitEthernet1/0/5 switchport

5. Quick port status overview

#show interfaces status

